<subSubSection id="09B16538FFD2FF8AE790FB40FBFBA7D8" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="411436B3FFD2FF8AE790FB40FBFBA7D8" blockId="4.[151,1135,1104,1506]" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">
<taxonomicName id="86AB4D30FFD2FF8AE790FB40FE97A72C" baseAuthorityName="Rossi" baseAuthorityYear="1790" box="[151,337,1275,1301]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="avidus">
<emphasis id="73DFEAA1FFD2FF8AE790FB40FE97A72C" box="[151,337,1275,1301]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Merodon avidus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est déjà mentionné par 
<bibRefCitation id="253A4B42FFD2FF8AE558FB40FC96A72C" author="Maibach A. &amp; Goeldlin de Tiefenau P. &amp; Dirickx H. G." box="[607,848,1275,1301]" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" pagination="110 - 140" refId="ref2935" refString="Maibach A., Goeldlin de Tiefenau P. &amp; Dirickx H. G. 1998. Syrphidae. In: Merz B., Bachli G., Haenni J. - P., Gonseth Y. (Eds.), Diptera - Checklist, pp. 211 - 224. info fauna - CSCF &amp; SEG ,, Neuchatel. Merz B., Bachli G. &amp; Haenni J. - P. 2001. Erster Nachtrag zur Checkliste der Diptera der Schweiz. Mitteilungen der Entomologschen Gesellschaft Basel 51: 110 - 140." type="journal article" year="1998">Maibach et al. (1998)</bibRefCitation>
, mais a été séparé depuis de l’espèce soeur 
<taxonomicName id="86AB4D30FFD2FF8AE652FAA5FD0FA70E" authority="(Wiedemann, 1822)" baseAuthorityName="Wiedemann" baseAuthorityYear="1822" box="[341,713,1309,1335]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moenium">
<emphasis id="73DFEAA1FFD2FF8AE652FAA5FE25A70E" box="[341,483,1310,1335]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">M. moenium</emphasis>
(Wiedemann, 1822)
</taxonomicName>
= 
<taxonomicName id="86AB4D30FFD2FF8AE5D8FAA5FC89A70E" baseAuthorityName="Rossi" baseAuthorityYear="1790" box="[735,847,1309,1335]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="avidus">
<emphasis id="73DFEAA1FFD2FF8AE5D8FAA5FC89A70E" box="[735,847,1309,1335]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">M. avidus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Taxon B sensu 
<bibRefCitation id="253A4B42FFD2FF8AE4F9FAA6FEE6A760" author="Milankov V. &amp; Vujic A. &amp; Ludoski J." pageId="4" pageNumber="127" pagination="15 - 24" refId="ref3060" refString="Milankov V., Vujic A. &amp; Ludoski J. 2001. Genetic divergence among cryptic taxa of Merodon avidus (Rossi, 1790) (Diptera: Syrphidae). International Journal of Dipterological Research 12: 15 - 24." type="journal article" year="2001">Milankov et al. (2001)</bibRefCitation>
et il n’était pas clair si les deux espèces étaient présentes sur le territoire suisse. La présence de 
<taxonomicName id="86AB4D30FFD2FF8AE6A1FAD9FDF1A742" baseAuthorityName="Wiedemann" baseAuthorityYear="1822" box="[422,567,1378,1403]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moenium">
<emphasis id="73DFEAA1FFD2FF8AE6A1FAD9FDF1A742" box="[422,567,1378,1403]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">M. moenium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
dans le canton de 
<collectingRegion id="836FF851FFD2FF8AE41FFADAFCA9A742" box="[792,879,1377,1403]" country="Switzerland" name="Geneve" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Genève</collectingRegion>
a été mentionnée par 
<bibRefCitation id="253A4B42FFD2FF8AE790FA38FEB9A7A4" author="Speight M. C. D. &amp; Athanasiades A. &amp; Bessat M. &amp; De Carvalho A. G. &amp; Faye J. - D. &amp; Fleury D. &amp; Monod V. &amp; Nicolas K. &amp; Passaseo A. &amp; Petremand G. &amp; Rochefort S. &amp; Castella E." box="[151,383,1411,1437]" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" pagination="87 - 98" refId="ref3556" refString="Speight M. C. D., Athanasiades A., Bessat M., De Carvalho A. G., Faye J. - D., Fleury D., Monod V., Nicolas K., Passaseo A., Petremand G., Rochefort S. &amp; Castella E. 2019. Revision de la liste des Dipteres Syrphidae du canton de Geneve, incluant cinq especes nouvelles pour la Suisse. Entomo Helvetica 12: 87 - 98." type="journal article" year="2019">Speight et al. (2019)</bibRefCitation>
et celle de 
<taxonomicName id="86AB4D30FFD2FF8AE50FFA3FFDBDA7A4" baseAuthorityName="Rossi" baseAuthorityYear="1790" box="[520,635,1411,1437]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="avidus">
<emphasis id="73DFEAA1FFD2FF8AE50FFA3FFDBDA7A4" box="[520,635,1411,1437]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">M. avidus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est à présent confirmée pour le 
<collectingRegion id="836FF851FFD2FF8AE4F0FA38FB85A7A4" box="[1015,1091,1411,1437]" country="Switzerland" name="Ticino" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Tessin</collectingRegion>
. La séparation de ces deux espèces cryptiques selon la morphologie est cependant remise en question et ces données doivent être considérées avec prudence (
<bibRefCitation id="253A4B42FFD2FF8AE49FFA7CFBF4A7D8" author="Speight M. C. D." box="[920,1074,1479,1505]" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" refId="ref3524" refString="Speight M. C. D. 2020. Species accounts of European Syrphidae (Diptera), Vol. 104. Syrph the Net Publications, Dublin, 314 pp." type="book" year="2020">Speight 2020</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
